    <date day="04" month="March" year="2017"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>The IETF will stop working on IPv4, except where needed to mitigate
   documented security issues, to facilitate the transition to IPv6, or
   to enable IPv4 decommissioning.</t>
    </abstract>
